<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1133258-anyone-else-find-this-book-after-reading">Anyone else find this book after reading Mitchell&#39;s Ghostwritten? I wasn&#39;t aware of its existence but in the week after first reading Ghostwritten and doing some wiki-reading into the gas attacks, I found this book at a used bookstore. Only just now getting into it, about a third of the way in so far. Really enjoying it but of course the similarity of the subject was very chilling at that moment.</a>
</div>
